description: Chay J's is a gourmet confections company specializing in New Orleans candies! Home of the AWARD-winning Original CREOLE PRETZELS-sweet & salty, buttery, praline caramel-toffee pretzels with pecans!Our mission is to please the most discerning palette by creating the most memorable culinary experience. Allow us to create a party in your mouth by bringing a little piece of NEW ORLEANS to your door!
name: Chay Js
